{"tid":2146422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【老豆搵仔新功能：搵出你身邊潛在被制裁對象】避開金錢來往，防止自己都成為被制裁對象","createTime":"2020-08-08T14:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T12:24:50.000Z","uid":285195,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb1197a3f9498c9dc2dadb9018ff1834a887da1","tid":2146422,"uid":285195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:31:10.000Z","msg":"第N輪被制裁名單潛在高危對象：<br />\n-黑警<br />\n-香港各紀律部隊人員(消防救護照計就應該低危啲掛)<br />\n-律政署某層級以上職員<br />\n-DQ事務主任<br />\n-各港共政黨任何記名成員<br />\n-金管局某層級以上職員<br />\n-MPFA某層級以上職員<br />\n-任何有證據顯示阻撓香港人取回MPF之公司某層級以上職員<br />\n-各中資銀行某層級以上職員<br />\n-HSBC，渣打，東亞某層級以上職員<br />\n-中資新聞機構從業員，隨時唔知係咪情報人員，特別大公文匯(當然明報CCTVB等前線人員就大部份都黃)<br />\n-任何發表過明顯監屎言論，甚至恐怖主義級數言論人士，而且被保留證據。例如石鏡泉<br />\n<br />\n如果閣下身邊有以上人物，請自行衡量，閣下同以上人物作任何金錢，服務上來往既時候，會唔會因為留有任何形式單據紀錄，而被捉黃腳雞，指控你對被制裁人士提供服務或進行金錢來往，被對方威脅要同你攬炒。<br />\n<br />\n當然，金額太細的，美國都唔得閒理。但點先為止金額太細呢？咁就唔識答你喇。總之明顯係有番咁上下數量金額既情況，好似樓宇買賣，簽租約，恒常生意來往，甚至買賣車輛等等，自己小心為上。<br />\n<br />\n符各國篤灰列表：<br />\n<br />\n英國間碟MI5: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/report-suspicious-activity-to-mi5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Freport-suspicious-activity-to-mi5&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=e399d635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/report-suspicious-activity-to-mi5</a><br />\n英國移民局:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amsallegations.homeoffice.gov.uk/default.aspx/RenderForm/?F.Name=Lf62UB7cz4C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amsallegations.homeoffice.gov.uk%2Fdefault.aspx%2FRenderForm%2F%3FF.Name%3DLf62UB7cz4C&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=b4d871d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amsallegations.homeoffice.gov.uk/default.aspx/RenderForm/?F.Name=Lf62UB7cz4C</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/report-immigration-crime\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Freport-immigration-crime&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=07137a19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/report-immigration-crime</a><br />\n<br />\n美國間碟FBI: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fbi.gov/tips\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fbi.gov%2Ftips&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=944552fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fbi.gov/tips</a><br />\n美國移民局: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uscis.gov/report-fraud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscis.gov%2Freport-fraud&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=b289ee69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uscis.gov/report-fraud</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲間碟ASIS: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asio.gov.au/counter-espionage.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asio.gov.au%2Fcounter-espionage.html&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=f20a1481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.asio.gov.au/counter-espionage.html</a><br />\n澳洲移民局: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.homeaffairs.gov.au/help-and-support/departmental-forms/online-forms/border-watch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.homeaffairs.gov.au%2Fhelp-and-support%2Fdepartmental-forms%2Fonline-forms%2Fborder-watch&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=7807351a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.homeaffairs.gov.au/help-and-support/departmental-forms/online-forms/border-watch</a><br />\n<br />\n加拿大間碟CSIS:  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/security-intelligence-service/corporate/reporting-national-security-information.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fsecurity-intelligence-service%2Fcorporate%2Freporting-national-security-information.html&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=bfac35c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.canada.ca/en/security-intelligence-service/corporate/reporting-national-security-information.html</a><br />\n加拿大移民局: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/protect-fraud/report-fraud.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fimmigration-refugees-citizenship%2Fservices%2Fprotect-fraud%2Freport-fraud.html&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=49344bbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/protect-fraud/report-fraud.html</a><br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭NZSIS: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nzsis.govt.nz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nzsis.govt.nz&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=997d58bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nzsis.govt.nz</a><br />\n紐西蘭移民局:  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.immigration.govt.nz/about-us/policy-and-law/integrity-of-the-immigration-system/immigration-fraud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immigration.govt.nz%2Fabout-us%2Fpolicy-and-law%2Fintegrity-of-the-immigration-system%2Fimmigration-fraud&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=836a7325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immigration.govt.nz/about-us/policy-and-law/integrity-of-the-immigration-system/immigration-fraud</a>"},{"pid":"b857897db687fa581589441e551087d35cb10a1b","tid":2146422,"uid":270428,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p7DyDGN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp7DyDGN.jpg&h=626415d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5a29e6d68e2a705f075e9fe184befa6c93ff9f3","tid":2146422,"uid":319942,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"香港政府出糧俾佢哋，咁咪制裁香港政府，凍結香港政府資金，到時全港公務員都失業，真攬炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64eb623c8714204787914f06c86af58d38f7a36a","tid":2146422,"uid":285195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci